Package bsiopis.webapp.entity

Class Address

java.lang.Object
bsiopis.webapp.entity.Address
@Entity public class Address extends Object
Address Entity Class. The secondaryEntity class of the application, it consists of the two non-mandatory address values of the user. Connects with the database columns via Hibernate annotations. It is mapped to the User Entity via One-to-One mapping.

2022-12-15
